# 1Ô∏è‚É£9Ô∏è‚É£ COMMON FAILURE POINTS

‚ùå Budget checked only at start, not at amendment
‚ùå Manual override allowed without logging
‚ùå No real-time commitment tracking
‚ùå No forecasting integration
‚ùå Payment released without commitment validation
‚ùå Separate procurement and finance systems

